{"tid":843212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"市道冷清 尖沙咀名店人龍不復再","createTime":"2018-10-01T03:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T05:38:32.000Z","uid":130626,"like":39,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"411904d22b107fdb537cebdcc94fa93de8f65588","tid":843212,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lckCN6MRc.9fFRG9rYjllQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/d1c4dd3726687e34a85dc44b42b977d6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FlckCN6MRc.9fFRG9rYjllQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fd1c4dd3726687e34a85dc44b42b977d6&h=6ee30e46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rpGdlUthospjeMQZvgUg.w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/ca25ca77a467f01fe2d6ad203e9548df\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FrpGdlUthospjeMQZvgUg.w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fca25ca77a467f01fe2d6ad203e9548df&h=139095c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OsXJ.zpOV8lsid2A3vqp2g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/bec13f7d536c35669b8d981ac7ed86ac\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FOsXJ.zpOV8lsid2A3vqp2g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fbec13f7d536c35669b8d981ac7ed86ac&h=4471d376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【本報訊】尖沙咀以往每逢十一長假，名店及藥房外均有大批內地旅客拖篋排長龍，但今年的情況則相對顯得冷清，不單赴港豪客減少，連到藥房買藥品、化妝品的內地客亦疏落。有內地客稱明顯感覺人流少，但香港擁有交通方便及匯率優惠等優勢，相信對內地遊客仍有吸引力。旅遊業議會預計，今年十一期間平均每日有一百三十個內地團抵港，與去年相若。<br />\n<br />\n昨日是十一長假開始前的周日，以往尖沙咀一帶遊客眾多，不過昨日所見，不論名店林立的廣東道，還是普通藥房，人流都明顯較往年稀少，雖仍有部分內地旅客在藥房門前執拾戰利品，但與以往門庭若市的情況相差甚遠。<br />\n<br />\n江蘇遊客指來港飛機多空位<br />\n來自江蘇的張先生預算來港花十萬元購物，感覺名店排隊人流明顯沒以往那麼擠迫，店內環境亦較鬆動。同樣來自江蘇的戴小姐和畢先生也指，今年十一人流少了，以往即使平日搭飛機來港，座位都會爆滿，但今次飛機上仍有很多空位。<br />\n<br />\n旅議會估計，今年七天的十一假期內平均每日有一百三十個內地團抵港，最高峰一日則可達二百團，與去年相若，而個人遊旅客數目則較去年有所增長。旅議會總幹事陳張樂怡指出，由於十一假期期間酒店房價較貴，故旅行團數目不多。<br />\n<br />\n珠寶業：貿戰及人幣貶值拖累<br />\n有珠寶集團負責人對十一假期營業額不表樂觀，指中美貿易戰及人民幣貶值拖累業務，十一的生意額若只錄單位數跌幅，「已經要拍手慶賀」。但周生生大中華區營運總經理劉克斌認為，八月起金價下跌，吸引旅客趁低價掃金，料十一生意額可有雙位數字增長。香港餐務管理協會主席梁振華亦對市道感樂觀，預計十一的整體生意額可按年增長百分之二至三。"},{"pid":"e5f0f0ae26114bc4e516ec1e546963e60eb1bb21","tid":843212,"uid":132587,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"年年都咁講架啦<br />\n宜家平日weekend都大把人排隊<br />\n真係懷疑佢地係咪唔洗番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141cbfad741045169ea592370d08a0805b188a20","tid":843212,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18f77aa9ee0029583fc32506a84852c63fa70139","tid":843212,"uid":164932,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"141cbfad741045169ea592370d08a0805b188a20","tid":843212,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e5f0f0ae26114bc4e516ec1e546963e60eb1bb21","tid":843212,"uid":132587,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"年年都咁講架啦<br />\n宜家平日weekend都大把人排隊<br />\n真係懷疑佢地係咪唔洗番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T04:02:22.000Z","msg":"間間都好撚多人排"},{"pid":"2f5305bdb553e585d8b758711fc8d5e3276c4ace","tid":843212,"uid":31431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"141cbfad741045169ea592370d08a0805b188a20","tid":843212,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score"